<li id="cite_note-Vance-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Vance_8-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Vance_8-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFVance2003" class="citation journal cs1">Vance, Mary Lee (2003). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1056%2FNEJMp020186">"Can Growth Hormone Prevent Aging?"</a>. <i>New England Journal of Medicine</i>. <b>348</b> (9): 779–780. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1056%2FNEJMp020186">10.1056/NEJMp020186</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12606731">12606731</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=New+England+Journal+of+Medicine&amp;rft.atitle=Can+Growth+Hormone+Prevent+Aging%3F&amp;rft.volume=348&amp;rft.issue=9&amp;rft.pages=779-780&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1056%2FNEJMp020186&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F12606731&amp;rft.aulast=Vance&amp;rft.aufirst=Mary+Lee&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1056%252FNEJMp020186&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHGH+controversies" class="Z3988"></span></span>
